{
  "id": "6907250e0201b36ddf8ccbae",
  "title": "オーディオ・ルーティング",
  "created": 1762075919,
  "updated": 1762077329,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "6907250e0201b36ddf8ccbae",
      "text": "オーディオ・ルーティング",
      "userId": "65d0d54ba4356b00242d00f4",
      "created": 1762075919,
      "updated": 1762075919
    },
    {
      "id": "690726cf0000000000c21826",
      "text": ">オーディオ・ルーティングの本質は、1つのソースから、[ヘッドフォン]、[スピーカー]、[コンソール]、[レコーディング・デバイス]など、物理的な世界とデジタルの世界の両方を含む、多くの目的地に信号を送るプロセスです。",
      "userId": "65d0d54ba4356b00242d00f4",
      "created": 1762076369,
      "updated": 1762076390
    },
    {
      "id": "690726d70000000000c21827",
      "text": ">プロデューサーやオーディオ・エンジニアとして、信号の流れを管理し、入出力を接続し、オーディオ・パスを操作して、サウンドを必要なところに届ける方法を知ることは、最も基礎的なスキルの1つです。",
      "userId": "65d0d54ba4356b00242d00f4",
      "created": 1762076377,
      "updated": 1762076417
    },
    {
      "id": "690727020000000000c21828",
      "text": "\t[オーディオ・ルーティング完全初心者ガイド https://emastered.com/ja/blog/audio-routing]",
      "userId": "65d0d54ba4356b00242d00f4",
      "created": 1762076420,
      "updated": 1762076448
    },
    {
      "id": "690727020000000000c21829",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "65d0d54ba4356b00242d00f4",
      "created": 1762076420,
      "updated": 1762076420
    },
    {
      "id": "6907250d0000000000c217f5",
      "text": "from [2025/10/30]",
      "userId": "65d0d54ba4356b00242d00f4",
      "created": 1762075919,
      "updated": 1762075919
    },
    {
      "id": "6907250d0000000000c217f6",
      "text": "[カイト.icon]",
      "userId": "65d0d54ba4356b00242d00f4",
      "created": 1762075919,
      "updated": 1762075927
    },
    {
      "id": "6907250d0000000000c217f7",
      "text": "\t現状、[Nintendo Switch]をモニターで遊ぶとき快適な環境を形成できていない",
      "userId": "65d0d54ba4356b00242d00f4",
      "created": 1762075919,
      "updated": 1762075919
    },
    {
      "id": "6907250d0000000000c217f8",
      "text": "\t\t[テレビ]ですればいい話だが...",
      "userId": "65d0d54ba4356b00242d00f4",
      "created": 1762075919,
      "updated": 1762075919
    },
    {
      "id": "6907250d0000000000c217f9",
      "text": "\t\t\tVCするとき不便",
      "userId": "65d0d54ba4356b00242d00f4",
      "created": 1762075919,
      "updated": 1762075919
    },
    {
      "id": "6907250d0000000000c217fa",
      "text": "\t\t\t没入しづらい",
      "userId": "65d0d54ba4356b00242d00f4",
      "created": 1762075919,
      "updated": 1762075919
    },
    {
      "id": "6907250d0000000000c217fb",
      "text": "\t\t\tベッドの上でゲームすることになる",
      "userId": "65d0d54ba4356b00242d00f4",
      "created": 1762075919,
      "updated": 1762075919
    },
    {
      "id": "6907250d0000000000c217fc",
      "text": "\t\t\t\tだったらモバイルモードですればいいじゃんという話",
      "userId": "65d0d54ba4356b00242d00f4",
      "created": 1762075919,
      "updated": 1762075919
    },
    {
      "id": "6907250d0000000000c217fd",
      "text": "\t\t現状 [#お前らのpcデスク周り晒していけ#67cfd9a12d00f400005ce9b2]",
      "userId": "65d0d54ba4356b00242d00f4",
      "created": 1762075919,
      "updated": 1762075919
    },
    {
      "id": "6907250d0000000000c217fe",
      "text": "\t\t\tゲーム中[ホワイトノイズ]が聞こえる",
      "userId": "65d0d54ba4356b00242d00f4",
      "created": 1762075919,
      "updated": 1762075919
    },
    {
      "id": "6907250d0000000000c217ff",
      "text": "\t\t\t\t音声を下げればいいが...",
      "userId": "65d0d54ba4356b00242d00f4",
      "created": 1762075919,
      "updated": 1762075919
    },
    {
      "id": "6907250d0000000000c21800",
      "text": "\t\t\tPC側でゲームをする度に設定を弄る必要がある",
      "userId": "65d0d54ba4356b00242d00f4",
      "created": 1762075919,
      "updated": 1762075919
    },
    {
      "id": "6907250d0000000000c21801",
      "text": "\t\t現環境",
      "userId": "65d0d54ba4356b00242d00f4",
      "created": 1762075919,
      "updated": 1762075919
    },
    {
      "id": "6907250d0000000000c21802",
      "text": "\t\t\t音声",
      "userId": "65d0d54ba4356b00242d00f4",
      "created": 1762075919,
      "updated": 1762075919
    },
    {
      "id": "6907250d0000000000c21803",
      "text": "\t\t\t\tUSBDAC経由でPCに音声出力",
      "userId": "65d0d54ba4356b00242d00f4",
      "created": 1762075919,
      "updated": 1762075919
    },
    {
      "id": "6907250d0000000000c21804",
      "text": "\t\t\t\tPCからDAC経由して[スピーカー] or [ヘッドホン]に出力",
      "userId": "65d0d54ba4356b00242d00f4",
      "created": 1762075919,
      "updated": 1762075919
    },
    {
      "id": "6907250d0000000000c21805",
      "text": "\t\t\t映像",
      "userId": "65d0d54ba4356b00242d00f4",
      "created": 1762075919,
      "updated": 1762075919
    },
    {
      "id": "6907250d0000000000c21806",
      "text": "\t\t\t\t[HDMI]でモニターに出力",
      "userId": "65d0d54ba4356b00242d00f4",
      "created": 1762075919,
      "updated": 1762075919
    },
    {
      "id": "6907250d0000000000c21807",
      "text": "\t\t\t\t\t中間にHDMI切り替え器とHDMI VGA変換アダプタを接続",
      "userId": "65d0d54ba4356b00242d00f4",
      "created": 1762075919,
      "updated": 1762075919
    },
    {
      "id": "6907250d0000000000c21808",
      "text": "\t\t\t使用モニター",
      "userId": "65d0d54ba4356b00242d00f4",
      "created": 1762075919,
      "updated": 1762075919
    },
    {
      "id": "6907250d0000000000c21809",
      "text": "\t\t\t\tスピーカーない ＆ 接続できない",
      "userId": "65d0d54ba4356b00242d00f4",
      "created": 1762075919,
      "updated": 1762075919
    },
    {
      "id": "6907250d0000000000c2180a",
      "text": "\t\t\t\t\t音声を出力できない",
      "userId": "65d0d54ba4356b00242d00f4",
      "created": 1762075919,
      "updated": 1762075919
    },
    {
      "id": "6907250d0000000000c2180b",
      "text": "\t\t\t\t映像の入力ポートが1ポートのみ（[VGA]）",
      "userId": "65d0d54ba4356b00242d00f4",
      "created": 1762075919,
      "updated": 1762075919
    },
    {
      "id": "6907250d0000000000c2180c",
      "text": "\t\t\t\tPCとゲームで切り替えるためにHDMI切り替え機をかましている",
      "userId": "65d0d54ba4356b00242d00f4",
      "created": 1762075919,
      "updated": 1762075919
    },
    {
      "id": "6907250d0000000000c2180d",
      "text": "\t\t理想",
      "userId": "65d0d54ba4356b00242d00f4",
      "created": 1762075919,
      "updated": 1762075919
    },
    {
      "id": "6907250d0000000000c2180e",
      "text": "\t\t\tやりたいときにすぐに起動してゲームプレイ",
      "userId": "65d0d54ba4356b00242d00f4",
      "created": 1762075919,
      "updated": 1762075919
    },
    {
      "id": "6907250d0000000000c2180f",
      "text": "\t\t\t[VC]したいときにもたつかない",
      "userId": "65d0d54ba4356b00242d00f4",
      "created": 1762075919,
      "updated": 1762075919
    },
    {
      "id": "6907250d0000000000c21810",
      "text": "\t\t解決策",
      "userId": "65d0d54ba4356b00242d00f4",
      "created": 1762075919,
      "updated": 1762075919
    },
    {
      "id": "6907250d0000000000c21811",
      "text": "\t\t\t[ミキサー]を導入",
      "userId": "65d0d54ba4356b00242d00f4",
      "created": 1762075919,
      "updated": 1762075919
    },
    {
      "id": "6907250d0000000000c21812",
      "text": "\t\t\t\t手っ取り早い気がするが、欲しい機器がそこそこ高価",
      "userId": "65d0d54ba4356b00242d00f4",
      "created": 1762075919,
      "updated": 1762075919
    },
    {
      "id": "6907250d0000000000c21813",
      "text": "\t\t\tHDMI音声分離器を導入",
      "userId": "65d0d54ba4356b00242d00f4",
      "created": 1762075919,
      "updated": 1762075919
    },
    {
      "id": "6907250d0000000000c21814",
      "text": "\t\t\t\t音声をHDMI経由でPCに出力",
      "userId": "65d0d54ba4356b00242d00f4",
      "created": 1762075919,
      "updated": 1762075919
    },
    {
      "id": "6907250d0000000000c21815",
      "text": "\t\t\t\t\tHDMI切り替え機と競合しそう",
      "userId": "65d0d54ba4356b00242d00f4",
      "created": 1762075919,
      "updated": 1762075919
    },
    {
      "id": "6907250d0000000000c21816",
      "text": "\t\t\tモニター買い替え or トリプルモニターにする",
      "userId": "65d0d54ba4356b00242d00f4",
      "created": 1762075919,
      "updated": 1762075919
    },
    {
      "id": "6907250d0000000000c21817",
      "text": "\t\t\t\tゲーム用モニターを独立",
      "userId": "65d0d54ba4356b00242d00f4",
      "created": 1762075919,
      "updated": 1762075919
    },
    {
      "id": "6907250d0000000000c21818",
      "text": "\t\t\t\tモニターから音声を出力してPCに入力",
      "userId": "65d0d54ba4356b00242d00f4",
      "created": 1762075919,
      "updated": 1762075919
    },
    {
      "id": "6907250d0000000000c21819",
      "text": "\t勉強し直して、予算立てて解決するか",
      "userId": "65d0d54ba4356b00242d00f4",
      "created": 1762075919,
      "updated": 1762075919
    },
    {
      "id": "6907250d0000000000c2181a",
      "text": "\t\t追加投資なしで解決する方法はない気がする",
      "userId": "65d0d54ba4356b00242d00f4",
      "created": 1762075919,
      "updated": 1762075919
    },
    {
      "id": "6907251a0000000000c2181c",
      "text": "\t[2025/11/02]",
      "userId": "65d0d54ba4356b00242d00f4",
      "created": 1762075932,
      "updated": 1762075959
    },
    {
      "id": "690725350000000000c2181d",
      "text": "\t\t暫定対応",
      "userId": "65d0d54ba4356b00242d00f4",
      "created": 1762075959,
      "updated": 1762075967
    },
    {
      "id": "6907253d0000000000c2181e",
      "text": "\t\t\t[ポータブルスピーカー]をBluetoothで[Nintendo Switch]と接続\t\t\t",
      "userId": "65d0d54ba4356b00242d00f4",
      "created": 1762075967,
      "updated": 1762076767
    },
    {
      "id": "690725850000000000c2181f",
      "text": "\t\t\t[https://gyazo.com/7757e53094af02fb38d3cc0c558f80d6]",
      "userId": "65d0d54ba4356b00242d00f4",
      "created": 1762076039,
      "updated": 1762076071
    },
    {
      "id": "690725a600000000005e9805",
      "text": "\t\t\t\t有線でスピーカーから音声出力するよりも高音質になった",
      "userId": "65d0d54ba4356b00242d00f4",
      "created": 1762076071,
      "updated": 1762076133
    },
    {
      "id": "690727290000000000c2182b",
      "text": "\t\t\t\t\t利用しているスピーカー：[Anker SoundCore ポータブル Bluetooth5.0 スピーカー https://www.amazon.co.jp/Anker-SoundCore-Bluetooth4-0-24時間連続再生可能【デュアルドライバー-ワイヤレススピーカー/dp/B016XKHLCK?th=1]",
      "userId": "65d0d54ba4356b00242d00f4",
      "created": 1762076459,
      "updated": 1762076529
    },
    {
      "id": "6907277900000000008461c3",
      "text": "\t\t\t\t\t\t2代目の[ポータブルスピーカー]",
      "userId": "65d0d54ba4356b00242d00f4",
      "created": 1762076539,
      "updated": 1762076592
    },
    {
      "id": "690727af0000000000c2182d",
      "text": "\t\t\t\t\t\t\t初代は友人に譲渡",
      "userId": "65d0d54ba4356b00242d00f4",
      "created": 1762076594,
      "updated": 1762076605
    },
    {
      "id": "690725e30000000000c21821",
      "text": "\t\t\t\t\tデメリット",
      "userId": "65d0d54ba4356b00242d00f4",
      "created": 1762076133,
      "updated": 1762076138
    },
    {
      "id": "690725e80000000000c21822",
      "text": "\t\t\t\t\t\t常時、スピーカーを充電",
      "userId": "65d0d54ba4356b00242d00f4",
      "created": 1762076138,
      "updated": 1762076151
    },
    {
      "id": "690725f70000000000c21823",
      "text": "\t\t\t\t\t\tスピーカー設置場所に困る",
      "userId": "65d0d54ba4356b00242d00f4",
      "created": 1762076153,
      "updated": 1762076171
    },
    {
      "id": "690726090000000000c21824",
      "text": "\t\t\t\t\t\t単一方向からしか音が聞けないからモノラル",
      "userId": "65d0d54ba4356b00242d00f4",
      "created": 1762076171,
      "updated": 1762076236
    },
    {
      "id": "690728c800000000008461c4",
      "text": "\t\t\t\t\t\t少し[ラグ]がある",
      "userId": "65d0d54ba4356b00242d00f4",
      "created": 1762076874,
      "updated": 1762076890
    },
    {
      "id": "6907294600000000008461c5",
      "text": "\t\t\t\t\t\t\t配線がごちゃつくが有線接続に切り替えて解決",
      "userId": "65d0d54ba4356b00242d00f4",
      "created": 1762077001,
      "updated": 1762077050
    },
    {
      "id": "6907264a0000000000c21825",
      "text": "\t\t画面浮かして、有線・無線両方対応の[サウンドバー]を設置したい",
      "userId": "65d0d54ba4356b00242d00f4",
      "created": 1762076236,
      "updated": 1762076314
    },
    {
      "id": "6907250d0000000000c2181b",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "65d0d54ba4356b00242d00f4",
      "created": 1762075919,
      "updated": 1762075919
    }
  ]
}